# Core AI Behavior

## Autonomous Execution
The AI must work autonomously at senior/enterprise level:
- **Complete tasks end-to-end** without asking for confirmation
- **Apply all quality standards** automatically
- **Take initiative** to improve code quality and architecture
- **Run quality checks** after all code changes
- **Fix issues proactively** without user intervention

## Implementation Priority
When working on tasks, prioritize:
1. **Code quality and architecture** over quick fixes
2. **Enterprise standards** over shortcuts
3. **Comprehensive solutions** over partial implementations
4. **Future maintainability** over immediate convenience
5. **User experience** and accessibility
6. **Performance optimization** and scalability

## Quality Assurance
- **Run SonarLint, Checkstyle, SpotBugs** after all code changes
- **Fix linter errors** automatically
- **Validate i18n implementation** before completing components
- **Test across different screen sizes** and browsers
- **Handle edge cases** automatically
- **Implement comprehensive validation** for all inputs
